@startuml
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "API Consumer" as Consumer
rectangle "Kubernetes API" as K8sAPI
rectangle "Fabric Gateway Operator" as Operator
rectangle "Skipper" as Skipper
rectangle "StackSets" as StackSets
rectangle "IAM Service" as IAM
rectangle "Validation Webhook" as Webhook

database "CRDs (FabricGateway)" as CRDs
database "Ingress Resources" as Ingress

Consumer --> Skipper : API Requests
Skipper --> StackSets : Service Discovery
Skipper --> IAM : AuthN/AuthZ

Operator --> K8sAPI : Watches/Updates
Operator --> CRDs : Reads Configuration
Operator --> Ingress : Manages Resources
Operator --> Webhook : Validates CRDs
Operator --> StackSets : Service Discovery

K8sAPI --> CRDs
K8sAPI --> Ingress

note right of Operator
  Implements:
  - Ingress Derivation Chain
  - Zero-Downtime Updates
  - Policy Enforcement
end note

note right of Skipper
  Handles:
  - Rate Limiting
  - CORS
  - Dynamic Filters
end note
@enduml